{"tid":1345914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵車廂文宣：政權默許 警黑合作  港鐵幫兇 圍毆市民","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:45:09.000Z","uid":271676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6215541aa709f52e317b47bf9813c4697f51227e","tid":1345914,"uid":271676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪尋日單野太夜<br />\nfb ig雖然好多人講<br />\n但今朝身邊人又唔覺好多講<br />\n藍絲同事唔知係理虧<br />\n定真係淨睇cctvb唔知發生咩事都冇討論過<br />\n<br />\n總之 我地要宣傳到佢地冇得扮唔知<br />\n<br />\n係港鐵見到播緊cable news d人有望下<br />\n但跟住有廣播變左有畫冇聲<br />\n得返下面識郁個d文字新聞(唔撚識形容希望巴絲get到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地可唔可以將呢d新聞短句係車廂朗讀出黎做文宣<br />\n就算冇新聞播緊都可以自己作幾句短而精既句子 扮到報新聞咁<br />\n有ipad可以播埋片<br />\n<br />\nEg. PPRB總警司謝振中表示唔能夠完全認同警察同黑社會有勾結，即部分認同警黑有勾結。<br />\n<br />\n講完再叫下口號：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政權默許 警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n港鐵幫兇 圍毆市民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n淨整停港鐵 唔知我地因咩事不合作都冇用<br />\n唔係個個巴絲都有勇氣整停港鐵怕事可以做呢d<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住 宣傳重點唔係黑社亂打人　係警黑合作</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文筆唔好 拋磚引玉 集思廣益 歡迎提供好既新聞短句同口號<br />\n<br />\n利申：好撚嬲好想做d野既和理非"},{"pid":"6f6436005781aa1b303a38216078cf5e392bc6ae","tid":1345914,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"向Law Society投訴何君堯條仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345784</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65e863ecf97b12676060445ba69a404f7f2f9ebe","tid":1345914,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"黑警同黑社會根本蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"7d31af6c652b82b64b06e8dbc41e5bd7c0d75c9c","tid":1345914,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"中<br />\n問題唔單係黑社會<br />\n重點係<br />\n一方面政府黑社會黑警合作<br />\n一方面仲暴力驅散示威者"},{"pid":"21b0dc9d6c5114bba1e4f62d8e503827b9e95ed8","tid":1345914,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d31af6c652b82b64b06e8dbc41e5bd7c0d75c9c","tid":1345914,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"中<br />\n問題唔單係黑社會<br />\n重點係<br />\n一方面政府黑社會黑警合作<br />\n一方面仲暴力驅散示威者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"背後就係共產黨一手策劃"},{"pid":"06af92d6fb55aa748ac3d379e93666825a9424ff","tid":1345914,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推，宜家係關鍵時期動搖淺藍民意！<br />\n<br />\n【文宣重點】元朗上環兩條戰線一齊推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"396f79725a62b3412937a8bcca1895fed109ca3e","tid":1345914,"uid":271676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8208f3d77920e850de4259e5dc210341a40eb935","tid":1345914,"uid":271676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30dcfb1a0df93e74fefa680b15244eed57117ff6","tid":1345914,"uid":271676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1fb257e040b485b2fe016c2f0af49e290211fd","tid":1345914,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f6436005781aa1b303a38216078cf5e392bc6ae","tid":1345914,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"向Law Society投訴何君堯條仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345784</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、</span></span><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以群眾鬥群眾</span></ins></strong>，內耗消耗民意，<br />\n引起眾多火頭，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>燃起多條戰綫，力圖模糊最初目標</ins></strong></span>，<br />\n大家要諗諗點拆<br />\n<br />\n或者好似另外一啲巴絲講，<br />\n陰謀論諗，可能借無差別攻擊事件自製亂象，繼而自己修補亂象，<br />\n繼而挽回民望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二、</span></span>另外大家可以 brainstorm 下：dress code 以顏色區分是否繼續可行？<br />\n如果著 smart casual 恤衫返工裝，<br />\n人人都係打工仔，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>人人都係 water</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n到時打，打打工仔，打平民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三、</span></span>除 TVB 有免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道外，<br />\nViuTV 同奇妙電視應該要同樣加開免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道，<br />\n本身兩台已有班底，只須加開頻道即可<br />\n甚至可考慮<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港首創本地 24 小時英語新聞頻道</span></ins></strong><br />\nRTHK 31 亦要加強推廣自身頻道<br />\n<br />\n同溫層講，大家都識得睇其他新聞，<br />\n但須知道好多酒樓、食肆冇嘢好播，咪播 TVB 新聞，<br />\n上年紀一輩只識打開對眼就睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四、</span></span>同樣唔可以忽視就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>境外酒店電視落地</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n大家打開酒店電視，睇香港嘅頻道，只會搵到 TVB，得 TVB 落到地，<br />\n呢方面要大家諗諗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>（外地人士第一觀感）</ins></strong></span>"}]}